This License governs the use, reproduction, and distribution of the DaoTi
XuanDun (道体·玄盾) LLM Firewall, comprising two categories of assets defined
below.
本许可证管辖道体·玄盾（XuanDun）LLM 防火墙的使用、复制和分发。该产品包含以下两类资产。
1. DEFINITIONS | 定义
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
1.1 "Repository Assets" means all files included in the public repository,
    including:
    (a) src/daoti_xuandun/reject_gate.py (reject gate core algorithm);
    (b) src/daoti_xuandun/preprocessors.py (preprocessing pipeline);
    (c) src/daoti_xuandun/config.py (configuration object with dynamic
        activity parameters);
    (d) src/daoti_xuandun/xuandun.py (main engine entry);
    (e) src/daoti_xuandun/luoshu_mapper.py (Luoshu symbol mapper);
    (f) src/daoti_xuandun/secure_strings.py (sensitive parameter protection);
    (g) src/daoti_xuandun/timing_checker.py (timing consistency checker);
    (h) src/daoti_xuandun/dynamic_shell.py (dynamic yin-yang shell);
    (i) src/daoti_xuandun/ancient_mapper.py (self-organizing symbol mapping);
    (j) src/daoti_xuandun/atlas_mapping.py (atlas mapping);
    (k) desktop/xuandun-desktop/engine_flask.py (engine Flask service);
    (l) desktop/xuandun-desktop/anti_debug.py (anti-reverse engineering
        detection);
    (m) desktop/xuandun-desktop/build_engine.py (Nuitka compilation script).
    "仓库资产" 指公开仓库中包含的所有文件，具体包括：
    (a) src/daoti_xuandun/reject_gate.py（拒绝门核心算法）；
    (b) src/daoti_xuandun/preprocessors.py（预处理管道）；
    (c) src/daoti_xuandun/config.py（配置对象，含动态活性参数）；
    (d) src/daoti_xuandun/xuandun.py（主引擎入口）；
    (e) src/daoti_xuandun/luoshu_mapper.py（洛书符号映射器）；
    (f) src/daoti_xuandun/secure_strings.py（敏感参数保护）；
    (g) src/daoti_xuandun/timing_checker.py（时序一致性校验）；
    (h) src/daoti_xuandun/dynamic_shell.py（动态阴阳壳）；
    (i) src/daoti_xuandun/ancient_mapper.py（自组织符号映射）；
    (j) src/daoti_xuandun/atlas_mapping.py（图谱映射）；
    (k) desktop/xuandun-desktop/engine_flask.py（引擎 Flask 服务）；
    (l) desktop/xuandun-desktop/anti_debug.py（反逆向检测）；
    (m) desktop/xuandun-desktop/build_engine.py（Nuitka 编译脚本）。
1.2 "Architecture Source Code" means the complete core algorithm
    implementation including original class names, detection logic, threshold
    parameters, and data processing pipelines. An obfuscated version of the
    architecture (Nuitka-compiled binary) is included in the repository
    with machine-code constants and no design-intent comments. The original
    Architecture Source Code with full design documentation is NOT
    included in the public repository and is protected as a trade secret.
    "架构源码" 指完整的核心算法实现，包括原始类名、检测逻辑、阈值参数
    和数据处理流水线。架构的脱敏版本（Nuitka 编译二进制）已包含在仓库中，
    使用机器码常量且不含设计意图注释。包含完整设计文档的原始架构源码
    不包含在公开仓库中，作为商业秘密受到保护。
1.3 "Documentation" means the written materials describing the theoretical
    foundations, detection methodology, experimental results, and system
    design, including but not limited to the Whitepaper and docs directory.
    "文档" 指描述理论基础、检测方法、实验结果和系统设计的书面材料，包括但不限于
    白皮书和 docs 目录。
1.4 "Encrypted Threshold Constants" means the pre-encrypted threshold values
    contained in src/daoti_xuandun/_key_generated.py (the SECURE_VALUES
    dictionary) and any derivative constants created through recompilation
    based on the original key.
    "预加密阈值常量" 指 src/daoti_xuandun/_key_generated.py（SECURE_VALUES 字典）
    中包含的预加密阈值，以及基于原始 key 通过重新编译产生的任何衍生常量。
1.5 "Academic Use" means use by an accredited educational or research
    institution for non-commercial research, teaching, or scholarly publication.
    Use by research divisions of commercial entities does not qualify as
    Academic Use.
    "学术用途" 指经认证的教育或研究机构为非商业研究、教学或学术发表目的而使用。
    商业实体的研究部门使用不构成学术用途。
    For the avoidance of doubt, research conducted by a university laboratory
    that receives funding from a commercial entity qualifies as Academic Use,
    provided the research results are intended for scholarly publication and
    the core algorithm is not transferred to the funding entity for its
    independent use.
    为避免疑义，接受商业实体资助的大学实验室所进行的研究属于学术用途，
    前提是研究成果旨在学术发表，且核心算法未转让给资助实体供其独立使用。
1.6 "Commercial Use" means any use that generates revenue or provides
    competitive advantage in a commercial context, including but not limited to:
    (a) integration into a product or service offered for sale or subscription;
    (b) use as a component of a revenue-generating system;
    (c) use by a for-profit entity in its operations;
    (d) provision of LLM input detection as a service.
    "商业用途" 指在商业背景下产生收入或提供竞争优势的任何使用，包括但不限于：
    (a) 集成至销售或订阅形式提供的产品或服务中；
    (b) 作为营利系统的组成部分使用；
    (c) 由营利性实体在其运营中使用；
    (d) 以 LLM 输入检测即服务形式提供。
1.7 "Redistribution" means making the core algorithm binary available for
    download, access, or use by any third party, whether through a public
    repository, private distribution channel, cloud API, or any other means.
    "再分发" 指通过公开仓库、私密分发渠道、云端API或任何其他方式，
    使核心算法二进制可供任何第三方下载、访问或使用。
2. TIERED LICENSE GRANT | 分层授权
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
2.1 REPOSITORY ASSETS — PUBLIC USE LICENSE
    Subject to the terms of this License, you are granted a worldwide,
    royalty-free, non-exclusive license to:
    (a) use, reproduce, and distribute the Repository Assets;
    (b) use the core algorithm for LLM input detection, including
        in commercial applications;
    (c) create derivative works based on the public API interface;
    (d) publicly display and perform the Documentation;
    provided that:
    (i)   you retain all copyright, patent, trademark notices, and this
          License in all copies;
    (ii)  you clearly attribute 独立研究者，知白 as the original author;
    (iii) any derivative works of the public API are distributed under
          this same License;
    (iv)  you do NOT reverse-engineer, decompile, or attempt to reconstruct
          the Architecture Source Code from the Nuitka-compiled binary or
          the Repository Assets;
    (v)   you do NOT sublicense, resell, or redistribute the core algorithm
          binary (xuandun-engine) as a standalone product or as part of any
          distribution platform, repository, or marketplace without
          prior written consent from 独立研究者，知白;
    (vi)  any derivative work created through modification of the core
          algorithm shall also be distributed under this License.
    仓库资产 — 公共使用许可
    依据本许可证条款，您被授予全球范围内、免版税、非独占的许可：
    (a) 使用、复制和分发仓库资产；
    (b) 使用核心算法进行 LLM 输入检测，包括商业应用；
    (c) 基于公开 API 接口创作衍生作品；
    (d) 公开展示和执行文档；
    但须满足以下条件：
    (i)   在所有副本中保留所有版权、专利、商标声明及本许可证；
    (ii)  明确标注原作者为 独立研究者，知白；
    (iii) 公开 API 的衍生作品须依据本许可证分发；
    (iv)  不得从 Nuitka 编译二进制或仓库资产中进行逆向工程、反编译或尝试重建
          架构源码；
    (v)   未经 独立研究者，知白 事先书面同意，不得将核心算法二进制（xuandun-engine）
          作为独立产品或任何分发平台、仓库、市场的一部分进行转授权、转售或再分发；
    (vi)  任何基于核心算法修改产生的衍生作品均须依据本许可证分发。
2.2 ARCHITECTURE SOURCE CODE — CASE-BY-CASE AUTHORIZATION
    Architecture Source Code is NOT included in the public repository.
    Architecture Source Code is protected as a trade secret.
    Access to Architecture Source Code (core algorithm class definitions,
    detection logic, threshold parameters, data processing pipelines)
    requires a separate written authorization from 独立研究者，知白.
    架构源码 — 逐案授权
    架构源码不包含在公开仓库中。
    架构源码作为商业秘密受到保护。
    获取架构源码（核心算法类定义、检测逻辑、阈值参数、数据处理流水线）需要
    独立研究者，知白 另行书面授权。
    To request access | 获取授权：
    (a) Academic institutions in the Chinese mainland (中国大陆学术机构):
        Submit an Academic Use Agreement including institution name, research
        scope, and responsible PI. Free of charge.
        提交学术使用协议，包含机构名称、研究范围和负责人。免费。
    (b) Commercial entities in the Chinese mainland (中国大陆商业实体):
        Submit a Commercial License Application. Terms negotiated per use case.
        提交商业许可申请。按使用场景谈判条款。
    (c) Entities outside the Chinese mainland (中国大陆境外实体):
        Submit a detailed proposal including use case, entity background,
        and compliance declaration. Reviewed case-by-case.
        提交详细方案，包含用途、实体背景和合规声明。逐案审核。
