    (a) any entity or individual subject to technology transfer restrictions
        under applicable Chinese law;
    (b) any military, intelligence, or surveillance organization;
    (c) any jurisdiction where such transfer is prohibited.
    架构源码不得出口、再出口或转让至：
    (a) 受适用中国法律技术转让限制的任何实体或个人；
    (b) 任何军事、情报或监控组织；
    (c) 禁止此类转让的任何司法管辖区。
3.3 Any person or entity receiving Architecture Source Code under a separate
    authorization may NOT further distribute, sublicense, or transfer the
    Architecture Source Code to any third party without explicit written consent
    from 独立研究者，知白.
    任何依据另行授权获得架构源码的个人或实体，未经 独立研究者，知白 明确书面同意，
